{"tid":1471764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生［廢文抒情減壓區］","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:31:24.000Z","uid":29132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b952efd324acbb82f02b323d0b5adc000ead0ffb","tid":1471764,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢幾個月個腦成日出現呢篇野，以前當潮文睇，今時今日係事實。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81348d686e2110a12e552ae230c8600a09a58233","tid":1471764,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"有冇玉皇大帝拯救我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142eeb5acce6de62749268e5fe102b60e8eff142","tid":1471764,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"我當堂嚇一跳"},{"pid":"a0c657feaa7c021f7b7a1e26683e59ee311c344e","tid":1471764,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81348d686e2110a12e552ae230c8600a09a58233","tid":1471764,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"有冇玉皇大帝拯救我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"人人都可以係食神"},{"pid":"98b7b14b0fddbb493eda4b905616aff7e98b9ba4","tid":1471764,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0c657feaa7c021f7b7a1e26683e59ee311c344e","tid":1471764,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{